arStrings.szText: "I feel like I'm ripping in half..."
That’ll be the ritual. It’s what's keeping you in one piece. The Spirit Realm is constantly shifting, blending. You would, too, unaided.
That’s the beauty of this place. It’s raw energy, given life. Every stone, every drop of water, is no more “dead” than you are. Change—growth—is the only law that governs here.
It’s nauseating. It’s breathtaking. It’s alien, it’s primordial. And for spirits such as this handsome fellow, it’s the most natural thing in the cosmos.
If it helps, I feel the same pain. You’re handling it better than most first-timers—even for one untrained in our ways.

Now let's go. Whatever threatens Ah Bulan threatens the whole of this realm.
